ange, $|{\\rm y}| > 4$, and/or at\nvery low $k_{\\perp}$. We leave it as a challenge for the planned ALICE 3\nexperiment at the LHC to study these two contributions to soft photon\nproduction in $pp$ collisions. This could shed new light on the so called\n``soft photon puzzle'' in hadron-hadron collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Feb 2023 17:01:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2023 12:39:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
