 Energy Spectroscopic Instrument (DESI) survey,\nthe Maunakea Spectroscopic Explorer (MSE) and MegaMapper, which will make more\nprecise and accurate distance determinations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Feb 2023 06:07:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-16"}
