ational in IC 5146 Streamer.\nOverall, the Streamer can be recognized as the first reliable candidate of edge\ncollapse, HFSs, and intertwined sub-filaments together.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Feb 2023 07:22:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
