es the interlayer exciton interaction. Our work proposes a hybrid\nquantum platform enabled by robust opto-electronic-magnetic coupling, promising\nfor quantum interconnects and transducers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Feb 2023 12:16:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-16"}
